l.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9bd4ccda84fea68c687ca63da0f47e69a7d5d67","tid":2040433,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:03:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4fe6514f8985e87d341f189aa2cf8717ba0766e","tid":2040433,"uid":199622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:03:52.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"c0d4c03ddda72258503b77b67319ebc77a15fa68","tid":2040433,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:08:22.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我不希望有一日在這一個地方迫害其他人的就是我們的手足。"},{"pid":"b333a9ec3f92de76896f2b307a8e7b03c7bcfe06","tid":2040433,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c0d4c03ddda72258503b77b67319ebc77a15fa68","tid":2040433,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:08:22.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我不希望有一日在這一個地方迫害其他人的就是我們的手足。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:09:37.000Z","msg":"我有一種不祥的預感&hellip;&hellip;亞洲社會武裝革命而演變成人道災難是常態。"},{"pid":"3f9436a043bfb46279eda9cbb102acaf6edf21f9","tid":2040433,"uid":305083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:12:17.000Z","msg":"5毛既存在是已 fc 的事實, 呢班人收錢帶風向搞到網絡世界污煙章氣, block / 標籤是其中一個令人冇咁眼怨既最直接途徑<br />\n<br />\n低手5毛被無視得多, 為左個飯碗就會進化, 變成閒時是手足, 重要關頭變返5毛帶風向, 令人防不勝防.<br />\n所以, 有啲之前確認左係藍絲/5毛既, 我認為應該要繼續 block 繼續標籤化, 到緊要關頭呢班友群魔亂舞時, 就可以適時出來屌柒佢地,<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講咩理性討論包容不同意見, <br />\n閒時大家傾下運動方向冇問題, 重要關頭搞搞震既我建議一律視之為藍絲賣港共人士看待, 所有手足都應該要大力屌柒"},{"pid":"bb8e230e122382c74ebd71cbdac814392b507c2a","tid":2040433,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:18:44.000Z","msg":"[文宣手足請入]國安法文宣方向<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2040485\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2040485</a>"}],"pinned":{"pid":"8f572e1751d61997e22e398ca64d576010bd007e","tid":2040433,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T14:50:55.000Z","msg":"唔介意你推多幾下"}}